        <div class="flex-auto">
          <h5 class="h3 mt0 mb1 regular dark-blue">Chris Lee</h5>
          <h5 class="h4 mt0 mb1 med-gray regular">
              Interaction Designer, 
              <a target="_blank" href="https://www.google.com/chrome">Google</a>
          </h5>
          <p class="med-gray">I'm an interaction designer working on <a href="http://chrome.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">Google Chrome</a>. I think technology should help regular people do meaningful things. I craft things mostly with code, sometimes with paper, and with Photoshop only when necessary. You can find me on the web <a href="http://chrsl.net/" target="_blank">here</a> or in real life in San Francisco.</p>
